token_info.description: Welcome to Hic et Nunc!!! This is a collection of 23 welcome stickers created for new joiners on the Hic et Nunc Discord #welcome channel between 11-18 April 2021. 50% of proceeds will go to the H=N "EGG" Tezos faucet fund for new NFT artists looking to get started with hicetnunc.
